A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the life and memory of Artward Howard Jr.; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, the State of Georgia mourns the loss of one of its most distinguished citizens
3 with the passing of Artward Howard Jr.; and
4 WHEREAS, he gave inspiration to many through his high ideals, morals, and deep concern
5 for his fellow citizens, and the devotion, patience, and understanding he demonstrated to his
6 family and friends were admired by others; and
7 WHEREAS, he was a person of magnanimous strengths with an unimpeachable reputation
8 for integrity, intelligence, fairness, and kindness, and by the example he made of his life, he
9 made this world a better place in which to live; and
10 WHEREAS, a compassionate and generous man, Artward Howard Jr. will long be
11 remembered for his love of family, friendship, and community and will be missed by all who
12 had the great fortune of knowing him.
